on complex tasks. However, LLMs generate outputs autoregressively, leading to inevita...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.18009", "source": "arXiv NLP", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.18009v1/2603.18009v1/10182.png", "score": 12}, {"id": "oai:arXiv.org:2603.18045v1", "title": "RARE disease detection from Capsule Endoscopic Videos based on Vision Transformers", "summary": "Abstract: This work is corresponding to the Gastro Competition for multi-label classification from capsule endoscopic videos (CEV). Deep learning network based on Transformers are fined-tune for this task. The based online mode is Google Vision Transformer (ViT) batch16 with 224 x 224 resolutions. I...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.18045", "source": "arXiv CV", "image": null, "score": 11}, {"id": "oai:arXiv.org:2603.18067v1", "title": "DarkDriving: A Real-World Day and Night Aligned Dataset for Autonomous Driving in the Dark Environment", "summary": "Abstract: The low-light conditions are challenging to the vision-centric perception systems for autonomous driving in the dark environment. In this paper, we propose a new benchmark dataset (named DarkDriving) to investigate the low-light enhancement for autonomous driving. The existing real-world l...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.18067", "source": "arXiv CV", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.18067v1/2603.18067v1/images/main_lidar4_new.jpg", "score": 10}]}